  "organic": [
    {
      "title": "Eliud Kipchoge clocks 2:01:09 for world record in Berlin Marathon",
      "link": "https://www.boston.com/sports/sports/2022/09/25/kipchoge-clocks-world-record-in-berlin-marathon/",
      "snippet": "us on WhatsApp: Updates on the Celtics, Sox, Bruins, and Patriots The Kenyan star clocked 2 hours, 1 minute, 9 seconds to shave 30 seconds off his previous best mark of 2:01:39 set on the same course in 2018. Kenya's Eliud Kipchoge crosses the line to win the Berlin Marathon in Berlin, Germany, Sunday, Sept. 25, 2022. AP Photo/Christoph Soeder By CIARÁN FAHEY, Associated Press 2 minutes to read Share BERLIN (AP) — He’s done it again. Two-time Olympic champion Eliud Kipchoge bettered his own world record in the Berlin Marathon on Sunday. The Kenyan star clocked 2 hours, 1 minute, 9 seconds to shave 30 seconds off his previous best mark of ",
      "date": "2022-09-25 23:41:16"
    },
    {
      "title": "Why Eliud Kipchoge can't break the marathon world record in Boston",
      "link": "https://www.boston.com/sports/boston-marathon/2023/04/06/boston-marathon-world-record-eliud-kipchoge/",
      "snippet": "Despite its popularity and history, the Boston Marathon course does not comply with World Athletics rules regarding \"official\" records. Eliud Kipchoge after winning the Berlin Marathon in 2022 and ",
      "date": "2023-04-06 15:55:54"
    },
    {
      "title": "伦敦马拉松创奇迹:冠亚季军全破雅各布纪录,非洲选手刷新世界纪录",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_81369effaea41752",
      "snippet": "<p>伦敦马拉松再创奇迹,冠亚季军均刷新雅各布纪录,其中萨巴斯蒂安与科杰儿查双双突破2小时大关,非洲选手天赋惊世,世界纪录提升近一分钟</p><p>两小时对他们如同半马,普通跑者望尘莫及,心酸不已</p><p>人类全马首次破2小时</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.",
      "date": "2026-04-28 08:11:57"
    },
    {
      "title": "埃鲁德·基普乔格",
      "link": "https://baike.sogou.com/v63027676.htm",
      "snippet": "\"埃鲁德·基普乔格(Eliud Kipchoge,1984年11月5日-),出生于肯尼亚裂谷省南迪郡,肯尼亚男子田径运动员｡ 埃鲁德·基普乔格在2003年获得世界田径锦标赛5000米金牌;2004年获得国际田联世界田径总决赛男子3000米冠军;2005年在国际田联黄金联赛布鲁塞尔站比赛上,获得男子5000米金牌;2010年在钻石联赛多哈大奖赛上,夺得男子5000米冠军｡",
      "date": "2024-09-28 22:27:56"
    },
    {
      "title": "人类历史首次跑进2小时!打破马拉松世界纪录",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_35269edf40175252",
      "snippet": "</p><p>据@世界田联 消息,刚刚结束的伦敦马拉松男子精英组,萨巴斯蒂安·萨维在最后阶段甩开生涯首马的科杰尔查,跑出惊人的1小时59分30秒,打破基普图姆保持的世界纪录,成为人类历史上第一位在两小时内跑完马拉松正赛的选手!</p><p>获得亚军的科杰尔查同样打开两小时,1小时59分41秒创造人类首马历史最好成绩;雅各布·基普里莫获得季军,2小时00分28秒同样超越了基普图姆保持的原世界纪录!",
      "date": "2026-04-26 19:16:17"
    },
    {
